  "remarks": "Ihar Subotsin is a long-term close business associate of Alexander Shakutin. Ihar Subotsin has been working with Alexander Shakutin since the early 1990s and was also his assistant when Alexander Shakutin was a member of the Council of the Republic of the National Assembly of the Republic of Belarus and his deputy at the Belarusian Tennis Federation.",
